HEADWORD: investigatory
<hw>investigatory</hw> <pos>adj.</pos> <def>Of or pertaining to an
investigation; accomplished by investigation; designed to find
information or ascertain facts; <as>as, <ex>investigatory</ex>
committee; the <ex>investigatory</ex> excesses of the
prosecutor</as>.</def>⟦br⟧
<syn><b>Syn. --</b> fact-finding, investigative.</syn>⟦br⟧
